			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe morgue_us\" and \"oe COL_Butcher\", in either order\r\n- Walk over to the cage that Us is in\r\n- Use command \"oe morgue_cagesneak\": Chop will be blinded and Us' cage will be unlocked\r\n- Us will start looking for a player to follow: when they follow you, this AD will play."
				},
